timuli. Optogenetic mapping revealed that SC projections to the lateral posterior nucleus (LP) of the thalamus, a non-canonical polymodal sensory relay, are sufficient to mimic visually evoked fear responses. In vivo electrophysiology experiments identified a di-synaptic circuit from SC through LP to the lateral amygdale (Amg), and lesions of the Amg blocked the full range of visually evoked defensive responses. Our results reveal a novel collicular-thalamic-Amg circuit important for innate defensive responses to visual threats.","altmetric_jid":"4f6fa62f3cf058f610008259","authors":["Pengfei Wei","Pengfei Wei","Nan Liu","Zhijian Zhang","Xuemei Liu","Yongqiang Tang","Xiaobin He","Bifeng Wu","Zheng Zhou","Yaohan Liu","Juan Li","Yi Zhang","Xuanyi Zhou","Lin Xu","Lin Chen","Guoqiang Bi","Xintian Hu","Fuqiang Xu","Liping Wang"],"doi":"10.1038/ncomms7756","first_seen_on":"2015-04-09T20:35:03+00:00","funders":["niehs"],"issns":["2041-1723"],"journal":"Nature Communications","links":["http://www.nature.com/ncomms/2015/150409/ncomms7756/full/ncomms7756.html","http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/ncomms7756","http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/ncomms7756","http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25854147?dopt=Abstract&utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter"],"pmid":"25854147","pubdate":"2015-04-09T00:00:00+00:00","publisher":"Nature Publishing Group","publisher_subjects":[{"name":"Multidisciplinary","scheme":"era"}],"subjects":["biology","science"],"title":"Processing of visually evoked innate fear by a non-canonical thalamic pathway.","type":"article","volume":"6","mendeley_url":"http://www.mendeley.com/research/processing-visually-evoked-innate-fear-noncanonical-thalamic-pathway"},"altmetric_score":{"score":11.6,"score_history":{"1y":0,"6m":0,"3m":0,"1m":0,"1w":0,"6d":0,"5d":0,"4d":0,"3d":0,"2d":0,"1d":0,"at":11.6},"context_for_score":{"all":{"total_number_of_other_articles":5033253,"mean":5.9592311638698,"rank":414127,"this_scored_higher_than_pct":91,"this_scored_higher_than":4618048,